Name: Rabbit & Dominoes
About the game: Rabbit & Dominoes is a minimalist puzzle game, which you have to help the rabbit collect all the eggs, combining the Dominoes pieces together to get the number showing on the green square . (Those math classes never was so useful until now.) resources - 70 puzzles for you to solve - 70 easter eggs for you to help the bunny catch - multiple ways to solve the same puzzle - If you fail, the number will be red and the level will reset. - If you get the combination right, the number will be green. - If you get the combination wrong, the pieces will blink red, so you should change theirs positions.
